            <p>1. We check your Road Tax & MOT due dates for you</p>
            <p>2. We set-up your renewal reminders to notify you by email 28-days, 7-days & 1-day before your Tax & MOT due dates</p>
            <p>3. Plus, we email you a printable reminder disc you to display on your vehicle windscreen</p>

        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12">
            @Html.ActionLink("Remind Me Now", "TaxInformation", "Home")
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-7">
        <img src="~/Content/img/Untaxed_Car.jpg" class="img-responsive"/>
    </div>  
    
